data.description: Nice home off of Hillcrest Road with tons of space. It has an open floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 Florida rooms with a double garage. You have to check out this fantastic private backyard. It is perfect for entertaining with a super nice gazebo/pergola. The seller is leaving the storage building for the new owners.
